OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy with rain or
OL,6,Fshowers, some heavy, during the
OL,7,Fmorning. Rain will clear as the
OL,8,Fshowers become less frequent during
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBright spells and showers at
OL,12,Ffirst in the evening but a band of
OL,13,Fcloud and rain, some heavy, soon
OL,14,Fspreads northeast. This clears to
OL,15,Fshowers towards morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FA cloudy start with scattered
OL,18,Fshowers. The showers will clear as
OL,19,Fbright or sunny spells increase from
OL,20,Flate morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
