OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloud,
OL,6,Frain pushes northeast Saturday
OL,7,Fbecoming heavy at times later. A few
OL,8,Fshowers then rain spreads southeast
OL,9,FSunday. Rain clears Monday morning
OL,10,Fleaving the afternoon dry and bright.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
